c := NewClient(options...)
streamChan := c.Discover("publisher","service1")
stream := <- streamChan
// simple case
var rspMsg1
stream.Send(reqMsg1)
stream.Recv(&rspMsg1)
// parallel request
for i := 0; i < 3; i++
go {
ctx := stream.NewContext()
var rspMsg2
ctx.Send(reqMsg2)
ctx.Recv(&rspMsg2)
}
